	d natural patterns found in Nordic landscapes.\n\nNo experience necessary\
	; all materials are provided. This hands-on program offers a calm\, creati
	ve space to slow down\, try something new\, and leave with a finished piec
	e and skills to continue stitching at home.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.co
	m/events/#/details/youth-art-class-introduction-to-embroidery/18324436/202
	6-04-11T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Arts & Culture
