BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:WoDs94o11qATVXAMNHnsB
SUMMARY:Moomins' Sea Adventures & Tove and the Sea
DTSTAMP:20260411T040859Z
DTSTART:20260414T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Dive into the whimsical world of Moominvalley and the life of i
	ts creator\, Tove Jansson\, with *Moomins’ Sea Adventures* and *Tove and t
	he Sea*.\n\n*Moomins’ Sea Adventures* brings Moominvalley to life with ill
	ustrations and life-sized characters from the stories. In the center of th
	e exhibit is an interactive island complete with a lighthouse and rowboats
	 that invites visitors to imagine adventures of their own.\n\n*Tove and th
	e Sea* offers a more intimate counterpoint\, tracing Tove Jansson’s lifelo
	ng relationship with the Finnish archipelago through large-scale photograp
	hs and reflective texts.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/
	moomins-sea-adventures-tove-and-the-sea/18406909/2026-04-14T00\n\nFrom SEA
