DESCRIPTION:The Indoor Plant Festival returns to the Lynnwood Event Center 
	April 17-19\, 2026. This is the premier event in the pacific northwest for
	 plant enthusiasts. It brings over 25 vendors together selling wide variet
	y of plants for indoor growers. It includes plants such as orchids\, acroi
	ds\, cacti\, succulents\, begonias\, gesneriads\, carnivorous plants\, air
	plants\, and so much more. There will be plant societies from around the P
	NW with beautiful plant displays\, you don’t want to miss it! \n\nDates: \
	n\nFriday\, April 17 5:00 pm – 8:30 pm \\(Must purchase tickets no later t
	han April 3\\) \n\nSaturday\, April 18 10:00 am – 5:00 pm \n\nSunday\, Apr
	il 19 10:00 am – 3:00 pm \n\nTickets are $15 at the door or purchase a $12
	 weekend pass in advance online. Kids under 15 years of age are free. \n\n
