UID:nMkoXfUYCGtIR58pu63M0
SUMMARY:Cooking from Scratch: Skills\, Techniques & Recipes
DTSTAMP:20260411T040900Z
DTSTART:20260421T000000Z
DESCRIPTION:Learn how to cook like a pro! Build your confidence in the kitc
	hen while mastering essential cooking methods and techniques. \n\nWhether 
	you’re just starting out or already love to cook\, this fun\, hands-on cla
	ss will help you master the building blocks of great cooking. Learn how to
	 handle a knife with confidence\, prepare proteins\, and turn fresh vegeta
	bles and hearty starches into flavorful dishes. Explore the secrets behind
	 rich stocks and silky sauces\, as well as the magic of hydrocolloids \\(f
	or thickening and gelling\\). \n\nDiscover how to balance flavors with fin
	esse\, work efficiently with smart kitchen mechanics\, and keep things saf
	e and clean with proper sanitation. Come sharpen your skills\, boost your 
	confidence\, and enjoy the satisfaction of creating meals that truly shine
	.\n\nLearning Objectives\n\nCooking methods and skills\n\nKnife skills \n\
	nWorking with proteins\, vegetables and starches\n\nPreparing stocks and s
	auces\, and using hydrocolloids\n\nBalancing flavors\n\nKitchen mechanics\
	, sanitation and safety \n\nWho Might Enjoy This Class? \n\nHome cooks who
	 would like to cook better\, diversify what they make\, get better results
	\, and be more efficient with their time in the kitchen \n\nAnyone ready t
	o learn cooking fundamentals and improve their skills \n\nCompetent cooks 
	and professionals wanting to fill in gaps in their skills and learn from a
	 pro\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/cooking-from-scratch
	-skills-techniques-recipes/18345422/2026-04-20T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All E
	vents
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/cooking-from-scratch-skil
	ls-techniques-recipes/18345422/2026-04-20T00
LOCATION:Seattle Central College Continuing Education\, 1701 Broadway\, Sea
	ttle\, WA
