UID:VtpDHCiXsws4ATPOggWyZ
SUMMARY:Lunch & Learn April 2026
DTSTAMP:20260411T040901Z
DTSTART:20260421T181500Z
DESCRIPTION:Featured Speaker: Catherine M. White – Accelerated Results   \n
	\nTopic: My 24/7 Ai Assistant \n\n11:15am – 11:45am – Open Networking // B
	usiness Showcase Tables\n\n11:45am – Food Ready\n\n12pm – Meeting Starts\n
	\n1pm – Meeting Ends \n\nMember – $15 pre-pay or $20 the day of. For the p
	urpose of food planning\, the cut-off for pre-pay will be the Monday befor
	e the Tuesday meeting\, allowing us enough time to work with our lunch pro
	viders on numbers.\n\nGuests – $20 at all times. \n\n50/50 raffle: 1 ticke
	t/$5 or 5 tickets/$20!  \n\nAttendance and raffle tickets available for pu
	rchase below! \n\nSpeaker Bio: \n\nChamber Members are invited to submit a
	n application to show interest in having a display table at our Monthly Lu
	nch & Learn events! Price is only $30 and you’ll receive table space to sh
	owcase yourself and your business before\, during\, and after our schedule
	d Lunch & Learn meeting. We appreciate your support and know you will make
	 lots of connections. More details will be sent to you once you submit you
	r application. Payment will be required once your application is approved 
	and your showcase space is reserved. \n\nBusiness Showcase Application ava
	ilable here! \n\n \n\n  \n\nMember of our Chamber? Please use click the Ch
	amber Member PrePay option. This option goes away at 5pm the Monday before
	 the Meeting and Member Price goes up to $20. \n\nNot a Member of our Cham
	ber or registering after 5pm the Monday before the Meeting? Please select 
	the Chamber Guest option.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details
	/lunch-learn-april-2026/18520974/2026-04-21T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Even
	ts
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/lunch-learn-april-2026/18
	520974/2026-04-21T00
LOCATION:Mill Creek City Hall North\, 15720 Main Street\, Mill Creek\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-all
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - All Events
